      "content": "i don't even know why i'm still typing this lol. everything just feels so heavy. the lab results came back today and it's over. three years of work just... gone. i feel like i've spent my whole life building a person that doesn't even exist anymore. i'm just so incredibly tired of fighting. i just want everything to be quiet. i just want the noise to stop.",
